{noformat}
2015-03-06 01:18:56 ERROR 000000035 Topology | CHECK:null arn:euca:bootstrap:production:node:10.111.5.109/ ENABLED->ENABLED=ENABLED [Transition request state=ENABLED rejected because of an ongoing transition: State:name=arn:euca:bootstrap:production:node:10.111.5.109/:state=ENABLED:mark=true:transition=TRANSITION arn:euca:bootstrap:production:node:10.111.5.109/ #25605 ENABLED_CHECK ActiveTransition name=ENABLED_CHECK from=ENABLED/false to=ENABLED/false error=NOTREADY action=CHECK id=25605 startTime=Fri Mar 06 00:49:44 PST 2015]
